.PP
\fIError\fR can be \fIReason\fR, \fI{error, Reason}\fR, \fI{aborted, Reason}\fR, or \fIReason\fR. \fIReason\fR can be an atom or a tuple with \fIReason\fR as an atom in the first field.

.PP
The following examples illustrate a function that returns an error, and the method to retrieve more detailed error information:


