.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
The function mnesia:create_table(bar, [{attributes, 3.14}]) returns the tuple \fI{aborted,Reason}\fR, where \fIReason\fR is the tuple \fI{bad_type,bar,3.14000}\fR.

